{"snp4.9:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 4.9 ","snp4.9:0.2":"Magandiyasutta ","snp4.9:1.1":"“Disvana tanham aratim raganca, ","snp4.9:1.2":"Nahosi chando api methunasmim; ","snp4.9:1.3":"Kimevidam muttakarisapunnam, ","snp4.9:1.4":"Padapi nam samphusitum na icche”. ","snp4.9:2.1":"“Etadisance ratanam na icchasi, ","snp4.9:2.2":"Narim narindehi bahuhi patthitam; ","snp4.9:2.3":"Ditthigatam silavatam nu jivitam, ","snp4.9:2.4":"Bhavupapattinca vadesi kidisam”. ","snp4.9:3.1":"“Idam vadamiti na tassa hoti, ","snp4.9:3.2":"(magandiyati bhagava) ","snp4.9:3.3":"Dhammesu niccheyya samuggahitam; ","snp4.9:3.4":"Passanca ditthisu anuggahaya, ","snp4.9:3.5":"Ajjhattasantim pacinam adassam”. ","snp4.9:4.1":"“Vinicchaya yani pakappitani, ","snp4.9:4.2":"(iti magandiyo) ","snp4.9:4.3":"Te ve muni brusi anuggahaya; ","snp4.9:4.4":"Ajjhattasantiti yametamattham, ","snp4.9:4.5":"Katham nu dhirehi paveditam tam”. ","snp4.9:5.1":"“Na ditthiya na sutiya na nanena, ","snp4.9:5.2":"(magandiyati bhagava) ","snp4.9:5.3":"Silabbatenapi na suddhimaha; ","snp4.9:5.4":"Aditthiya assutiya anana, ","snp4.9:5.5":"Asilata abbata nopi tena; ","snp4.9:5.6":"Ete ca nissajja anuggahaya, ","snp4.9:5.7":"Santo anissaya bhavam na jappe”. ","snp4.9:6.1":"“No ce kira ditthiya na sutiya na nanena, ","snp4.9:6.2":"(iti magandiyo) ","snp4.9:6.3":"Silabbatenapi na suddhimaha; ","snp4.9:6.4":"Aditthiya assutiya anana, ","snp4.9:6.5":"Asilata abbata nopi tena; ","snp4.9:6.6":"Mannamaham momuhameva dhammam, ","snp4.9:6.7":"Ditthiya eke paccenti suddhim”. ","snp4.9:7.1":"“Ditthanca nissaya anupucchamano, ","snp4.9:7.2":"(magandiyati bhagava) ","snp4.9:7.3":"Samuggahitesu pamohamaga; ","snp4.9:7.4":"Ito ca naddakkhi anumpi sannam, ","snp4.9:7.5":"Tasma tuvam momuhato dahasi. ","snp4.9:8.1":"Samo visesi uda va nihino, ","snp4.9:8.2":"Yo mannati so vivadetha tena; ","snp4.9:8.3":"Tisu vidhasu avikampamano, ","snp4.9:8.4":"Samo visesiti na tassa hoti. ","snp4.9:9.1":"Saccanti so brahmano kim vadeyya, ","snp4.9:9.2":"Musati va so vivadetha kena; ","snp4.9:9.3":"Yasmim samam visamam vapi natthi, ","snp4.9:9.4":"Sa kena vadam patisamyujeyya. ","snp4.9:10.1":"Okam pahaya aniketasari, ","snp4.9:10.2":"Game akubbam muni santhavani; ","snp4.9:10.3":"Kamehi ritto apurakkharano, ","snp4.9:10.4":"Katham na viggayha janena kayira. ","snp4.9:11.1":"Yehi vivitto vicareyya loke, ","snp4.9:11.2":"Na tani uggayha vadeyya nago; ","snp4.9:11.3":"Jalambujam kandakavarijam yatha, ","snp4.9:11.4":"Jalena pankena canupalittam; ","snp4.9:11.5":"Evam muni santivado agiddho, ","snp4.9:11.6":"Kame ca loke ca anupalitto. ","snp4.9:12.1":"Na vedagu ditthiyayako na mutiya, ","snp4.9:12.2":"Sa manameti na hi tammayo so; ","snp4.9:12.3":"Na kammuna nopi sutena neyyo, ","snp4.9:12.4":"Anupanito sa nivesanesu. ","snp4.9:13.1":"Sannavirattassa na santi gantha, ","snp4.9:13.2":"Pannavimuttassa na santi moha; ","snp4.9:13.3":"Sannanca ditthinca ye aggahesum, ","snp4.9:13.4":"Te ghattayanta vicaranti loke”ti. ","snp4.9:13.5":"Magandiyasuttam navamam. "}